---
title: England's Winner Winner Chicken Dinner Burger with Red Onion Gravy and Honey Roasted Root Veg
description: "Come on England!" Show your support this Six Nations with burgers inspired by each team's homeland! An homage to the traditional English roast, this Winner Winner Chicken Dinner Burger is best served pitch-side with red onion gravy and sticky honey roasted root veg.
